    - target: {fileID: 5122842465899161861, guid: ed7b740a5cf36044ab197a19d1fe05ab, type: 3}
      propertyPath: m_text
      value: "Behold all the world's gardens and see \nthe traces of God's craft:
        \nwhere eyes of silver gaze on high, \nwith pupils made of molten gold, \non
        emerald stalks they testify \nthat God acknowledges no equal\n\nAbu Nuwas"
